window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When Daine comes down from the mountains, she carries with her two things: a dark secret about her own past, and a strangely powerful magic that even she doesn't understand.</p> <p>Soon Daine has a job working for Onua, the queen's horsemistress, who is astonished at the girl's way with animals. It's almost as if she can speak to them....</p> <p>Daine and Onua travel to Pirate's Swoop, where Daine finds herself swept into a war that threatens all of Tortall, a war where magic is one of the main weapons.</p> <p>The wall between the worlds is cracking.</p> <p>The magical creatures are returning.</p> <p>Now Daine must master her own magic, and face her own dark memories, if she is to save her new home from destruction.</p>"; 
